item.title: Need Help creating a bank booth thing
item.dc:creator: @r0ckstar96 r0ckstar96
item.description:
@r0ckstar96 wrote:

go in to client.java, do ctrl + f and type makeGlobalObject
You might need to click next 2 times
Under the first global object EXAMPLE: makeGlobalObject(2865, 9956, 2213, -2, 10); // Home bank
put

	makeGlobalObject(2709, 3487, 2213, 0, 10); // Bank Booth
